Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&H3CF1F3&\b0}影片壓制: 九洲客 　字幕調校: 子賀居士　招募Q號: 76846146{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}面試{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi. I've got an appointment with Mr. Ullman.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你好 我和尤爾曼先生有約{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Jack Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的名字是傑克·特朗斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His office is the first door on the left.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他的辦公室在一樓的左邊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ullman?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}尤爾曼先生?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Jack Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是傑克·特朗斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in, Jack.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快進來 傑克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Very nice to meet you. - Nice to meet you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 非常高興見到你 - 我也是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my secretary, Susie.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這是我的秘書 蘇西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Susie, how do you do? - Any trouble finding us?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 蘇西 你好 - 我們這兒很難找吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem at all. I made the trip in 3 1/2 hours.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不難找 到這兒我才花了三個半小時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very good time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}算是非常順利了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down a minute, Jack.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}請稍坐一會 傑克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just make yourself at home.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}隨意 不要拘束{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like some coffee?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要來點咖啡嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're having some, I wouldn't mind. Thanks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}方便的話 我想嘗一嘗 謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Susie. - Sure.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 蘇西 - 好的 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And ask Bill Watson to join us.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}順便請比爾·華生過來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really want to go and live in that hotel for the winter?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你真打算 整個冬天都住那個旅館嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure I do.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}當然我願意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be lots of fun.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那一定會很有趣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I guess so.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯 我也這麼認為{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, there's hardly anybody to play with around here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不過 那兒恐怕沒有人可以陪我玩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. lt always takes a little time to make new friends.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我知道 交新朋友總要花些時間的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess so.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯 恐怕是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Tony?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}托尼怎樣想呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's looking forward to the hotel, I bet.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他很期待去住那個旅館 我敢打賭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I ain't, Mrs. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}錯 我並不期待 特朗斯太太{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come on, Tony. Don't be silly.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好了 托尼 不要淘氣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go there.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不想去那個地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come you don't want to go?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你為什麼不想去呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只是不想而已{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just wait and see.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那我們走著瞧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all going to have a real good time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我相信我們會有個愉快的冬天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill, I'd like you to meet Jack Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比爾 這位是傑克·特朗斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do, Bill?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你好 比爾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Nice to meet you. - Pleasure to meet you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 非常高興認識你 - 很榮幸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab a chair, Bill. Join in.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}找個位子坐 比爾 我們開始吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack is going to take care of the Overlook for us this winter.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}傑克準備為我們 在這個冬天照顧遙望旅館{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to take him around soon as we're through.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等我們這邊告個段落 你就帶他去逛逛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack is a schoolteacher.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}傑克是位老師{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Formerly a schoolteacher.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}以前是位老師{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What line of work are you in now?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那你現在幹什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a writer.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}寫作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teaching's been more or less a way of making ends meet.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}光靠教書 收支還是平衡不了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ought to be quite a change for you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}對你而言 這是很大的轉變吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for a change.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我正是在尋求轉變{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our people in Denver recommended Jack very highly, and for once...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們在丹佛的人都強烈推薦傑克 而且我立刻就...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I agree with them.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}贊成了他們的意見{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, where were we?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那好 我們講到哪裏了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to explain...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我正打算解說...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that our season here runs from May 15th to October 30th.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們是在5月15號到10月30號營業{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we close down completely until the following May.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然後我們會歇業 直到下個5月來臨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind if I ask why you do that?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我可以問問是為什麼嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to me that the skiing up here would be fantastic.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就我所見 在這邊滑雪將是非常美妙的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be. The problem is the enormous cost...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那是肯定的 但是 問題在於龐大的開銷...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it would be to keep the road to Sidewinder open.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}為此我們必須保持道路通暢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a 25-mile stretch of road.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而道路綿延25英哩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gets 20 feet of snow during the winter.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}到了冬天 積雪會厚達20英尺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just no way to make it economically feasible...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要保持道路通暢的話...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to keep it clear.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}實在是沒有什麼經濟效益{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the place was built in 1907...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}自1907年這個地方被修建以來...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there was very little interest in winter sports.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很少有人對這兒的冬季運動感興趣的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This site was chosen for its seclusion and scenic beauty.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這個地方是因為它的 與世俗隔絕和風光明媚而聞名{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's certainly got plenty of that.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}當然 不只如此而已{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they give you any idea in Denver...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}丹佛的人有沒有告訴過你...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...about what the job entails?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}關於這個工作的負擔?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only in a very general way.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只說了個大概{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winters can be fantastically cruel.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}冬季總是難以想像的酷寒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The basic idea is to cope with the very costly damage...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}工作內容是維修工作 防止帶來重大損失...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and depreciation which can occur.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}和其它一些相關的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This consists mainly of running the boiler...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}其實主要就是要照顧鍋爐...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...heating different parts of the hotel on a daily rotating basis...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}每天都要加熱 保持旅館各個角落的溫暖...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...repairing damage as it occurs...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果有損壞發生就要修復...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and doing repairs so the elements can't get a foothold.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}持續維護使損壞無法產生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds fine to me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這對我而言是沒有問題的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Physically, it's not a very demanding job.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}其實上這工作 真的沒有什麼太高的要求{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that can get a bit trying here during the winter...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在這裏 冬季唯一真正要克服的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is a tremendous sense of isolation.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是巨大的被隔離感{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That just happens to be exactly what I'm looking for.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那正好是我要尋求的東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm outlining a new writing project.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我正構思一部新的作品{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five months of peace is just what I want.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}五個月的安靜生活 正符合我所需{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very good, Jack.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好 傑克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, for some people...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道 對某些人...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...solitude...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}...孤獨...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and isolation...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}...和隔離...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can, of itself, become a problem.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}...會是一個很大的問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}對我而言不是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about your wife and son? Do you think they'll take to it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那你的妻子和兒子呢? 你認為他們沒問題吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll love it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他們會喜歡的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I turn you over to Bill...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在我把你交給比爾以前...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's one other thing I think we should talk about.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想我還有一件事 不得不和你講{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to sound melodramatic...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是嚇唬人...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's been known to give a few people...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不過 這的確會讓某些人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...second thoughts about the job.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}重新考慮能否接受這個工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm intrigued.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我很感興趣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't suppose they said anything in Denver...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我認為 丹佛的人一定沒有提到這個...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...about the tragedy we had up here during the winter of 1970.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}1970年在這兒發生的悲劇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe they did.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他們的確沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My predecessor in this job...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的前任...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...hired a man named Charles Grady as the winter caretaker.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}僱傭了一個叫查爾斯·格瑞第 擔任冬季看管員的工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came up with his wife and 2 little girls of about 8 and 10.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他帶著妻子和兩個女兒 一個8一個10歲左右{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had a good employment record, good references.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他有著良好的工作記錄和介紹人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And from what I've been told, he seemed...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就我剛才所言 他似乎...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like a completely normal individual.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就像一個安全正常的人一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at some point during the winter...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是冬季的某天...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he must have suffered some kind of a complete mental breakdown.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他肯定受到了巨大的精神折磨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran amuck...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然後瘋狂地...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and killed his family with an ax.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}用斧頭 殺了全家人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stacked them neatly in a room in the west wing, and then...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}屍體全堆到西翼的一個房間裏...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he put both barrels of his shotgun in his mouth.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}來福槍裝了兩發子彈 含在嘴裏擊發{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police thought...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}警察認為...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that it was what the old-timers used to call cabin fever.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那就是以前所謂的幽閉恐慌癥{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kind of claustrophobic reaction which can occur...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一種幽閉式的反應 發生在...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when people are shut in together over long periods of time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}人被封閉在一起 經過一段相當長時間後{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這個故事...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...quite a story.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}實在很刺激{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still hard for me to believe it actually happened here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}到現在我還是無法相信 它就發生在這個地方 就是這兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it did.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是 它的確是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you can appreciate why I wanted to tell you about it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我相信你能理解 我為什麼要告訴你這些{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly can.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我當然可以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also understand why your people in Denver...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我還可以理解 為什麼丹佛的人...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...left it for you to tell me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}留著這件事 讓你來告訴我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, some people can be put off...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}顯然 一些人會退縮...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from staying in a place where something like that happened.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不願意待在發生過這種事的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can rest assured that's not going to happen with me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你可以放心 這不會發生在我身上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as far as my wife is concerned...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}至於我的妻子...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm sure she'll be absolutely fascinated when I tell her.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我確定告訴她以後 她一定會很著迷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a confirmed ghost story...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她是個忠實的鬼故事迷...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and horror film addict.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}...和恐怖片迷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tony, do you think Dad'll get the job?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}托尼 你認為爸爸會得到那份工作嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He already did.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他已經得到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to phone Wendy up in a few minutes to tell her.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他馬上就會打電話告訴溫蒂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hi, babe. - Hi, hon. How's it going?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 嗨 寶貝 - 嗨 親愛的 事情進行得怎樣?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great. I'm at the hotel and I still have a lot to do.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好 我還在旅館裏 而且還有許多地方還沒去看過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can get home before 9 or 10.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我認為9點或10點前 我可能到不了家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you got the job.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}聽起來你得到這份工作了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. It's a beautiful place.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯 這兒真是個漂亮的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Danny are going to love it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你和丹尼會喜歡上它的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tony, why don't you want to go to the hotel?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}托尼 你為什麼不想去那個旅館?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.02,0:11:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do too know. Now come on, tell me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道的 好了 告訴我吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要 我不想告訴你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}求求你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Tony, tell me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好了 托尼 告訴我吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hold your eyes still so I can see.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}現在睜開眼睛 我來檢查{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. Now the other one.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好 另一隻眼睛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}乖孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Danny...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 丹尼...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when you were brushing your teeth...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在你刷牙的時候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you remember if you smelled anything funny...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你記得你聞到一些怪味{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or saw any bright, flashing lights or anything at all strange?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或者看見閃光 和其它一些怪東西嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember when you were brushing your teeth?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那你記得你在刷牙麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the next thing you remember after you were brushing your teeth?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那麼 刷牙之後呢? 你記得發生過什麼事情嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom was saying, "Wake up. Wake up, Danny, wake up."\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}媽媽對我說 "醒醒 丹尼 醒醒"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you remember what you were doing...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那你能否記得在刷牙前...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just before you started brushing your teeth?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在做些什麼嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking to Tony.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}和托尼說話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Tony one of your animals?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}托尼是你的寵物之一嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He's a little boy that lives in my mouth.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是 他是住在我嘴裏的小男孩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tony's his imaginary friend.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}托尼是他想像中的朋友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to open your mouth now, could I see Tony?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}假如你現在張開嘴 我能看見托尼嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}為什麼不行?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he hides.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因為他藏起來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where does he go?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他藏在什麼地方?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To my stomach.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的胃裏面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Tony ever tell you to do things?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}托尼有要你去做過什麼嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to talk about Tony anymore.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不想再談論托尼了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Danny.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 丹尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask you to do me a favor...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要請你幫我個忙...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and stay quietly in bed for the rest of the day. Okay?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}今天都乖乖地待在床上 好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一定要這樣嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'd like you to.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 我希望你這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going in the other room for a few minutes and talk.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們要去另外的房間說幾句話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back and check on you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}之後我會來看你的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Shall we go into the living room? - Yes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我們去客廳嗎? - 是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Please. - Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 請坐 - 謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Torrance, I don't think you have anything to worry about.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}特朗斯太太 我認為你沒有什麼好擔心的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite sure there's nothing physically wrong with Danny.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我確信丹尼身體健康{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems absolutely fine now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他現在看起來非常好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you should've seen him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是你還是應該檢查一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids can scare you to death.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}孩子往往會嚇著你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But believe me, these episodes are not at all uncommon.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是相信我 那些並不算反常{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they look much worse than they are.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他們往往比表面看起來要好很多{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what was the matter with him?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是 他到底是怎麼了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the time, these episodes with kids are never explained.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}大多數時候 發生在小孩子身上 某些事情是無法依常理解釋的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're brought on by emotional factors and rarely occur again.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只是一些情緒上的原因 而且基本上很少再發生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're more akin to autohypnosis...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}和自我催眠很相似...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a kind of self-induced trance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一種自我誘導的恍惚狀態{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it reoccurs, which I doubt...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是 假如再發生的話 我認為...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we can always think about having some tests done.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們可以試著做些檢查{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're right.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我確信你是對的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been in Boulder long?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你住在博得很久了嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only about three months.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只有三個月左右{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're from Vermont. My husband was teaching school there.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們是佛蒙得州來的 我丈夫以前在那邊的學校教書{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the appearance of Danny's imaginary friend....\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}丹尼想像中的朋友出現在...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tony.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}托尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Tony's first appearance happen to coincide with your arrival here?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那麼 托尼的情況 最早發生在你們到這兒的時候嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see....\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想想...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Danny started talking to Tony...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}丹尼和托尼說話...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...about the time we put him in nursery school.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是在我們送他去幼兒園時開始的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he adjust well to school?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他適應學校生活嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't like it too much at first.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他最開始並不喜歡學校{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he had an injury, so we kept him out for a while and....\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是 之後他受了傷 然後我們就把他留在家裏一段時間...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's about when I first noticed he was talking to Tony.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這就是我最早 注意到他和托尼交談的時候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of injury did he have?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他受了什麼樣的傷?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He dislocated his shoulder.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}肩膀脫臼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did he manage to do that?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他怎麼會受這樣的傷?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just one of those things, you know.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這只是 嗯 那樣的一些事 你知道的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Purely an accident.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}完全是意外事故{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My husband had been drinking...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我丈夫喝醉...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he came home about three hours late.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然後比往常遲三個小時回到家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he wasn't exactly in the greatest mood that night.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他那天晚上 心情不太好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Danny had scattered some of his school papers all over the room...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然後丹尼把他一些教學用試卷 扔到滿屋都是...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and my husband grabbed his arm to pull him away from them.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}於是我丈夫就拉住他的肩膀 想讓他離開那些試卷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the sort of thing you do 100 times with a child...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就是這樣一些行為 你起碼對孩子做過上百次...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you know, in a park or in the street.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道的 平常在公園或者街道上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But on this particular occasion...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是當時有點失控...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my husband just used too much strength...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我丈夫用力過猛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he injured Danny's arm.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然後他傷著了丹尼的肩膀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, something good did come out of it all because he said...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}無論如何 負面的事也有一些正面意義 因為他說...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..."Wendy, I'm never going to touch another drop.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"溫蒂 我絕對不會再犯同樣的傻事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I do, you can leave me."\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}假如再發生的話 你可以離開我"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he didn't.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然後 他的確做到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't had any alcohol in 5 months.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他五個月沒再沾過一點酒精{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}旅館歇業日{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must really be high up. The air feels so different.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們肯定到了很高的地方 空氣都不太一樣了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}爸爸?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我餓了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've eaten your breakfast.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你應該吃了早餐的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get you something as soon as we get to the hotel.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等我們到了旅館就給你找些吃的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Mom.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it around here that the Donner party got snowbound?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就是在這附近 多納組織被雪給困住的吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that was farther west, in the Sierras.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我認為是在更西邊的地方 在山脊地帶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the Donner party?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什麼是多納組織?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were a party of settlers in covered wagon times.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他們是一個蓬車時代的殖民組織{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got snowbound one winter in the mountains.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}某個冬天他們被雪困在山裏頭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They had to resort to cannibalism in order to stay alive.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}導致後來他們相互殘殺當作食物 為的是讓自己能夠生存下來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean they ate each other up?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的意思是他們相互吃掉別人?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They had to, in order to survive.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}為了活命 他們不得不這樣做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}傑克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Mom.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要擔心 媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all about cannibalism. I saw it on TV.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我知道人吃人的 在電視上看過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, it's okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看 我說沒什麼吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He saw it on the television.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他在電視上都看過了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What time does the plane leave? - 8:30.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 飛機什麼時候起飛? - 8點30分{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That gives us plenty of time to go over everything.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這樣我們就有充足的時間 可以仔細檢查每樣東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Goodbye, Mr. Ullman. - Bye.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 再見 尤爾曼先生 - 再見{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:20:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning. I hope you haven't been waiting too long.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}早安 希望沒有讓你等太久{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. We had time to grab a bite to eat.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}沒關係 我們正好有足夠的時間去找點吃的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Glad you made it before they shut down the kitchen.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很幸運 你能趕在他們關掉廚房前這樣做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your family having a look around?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的家人都有四處看看嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, my son's discovered the games room.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}沒有 因為我兒子發現了遊戲室{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Has your luggage been brought in? - Right there.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你的行李都帶來了嗎? - 都在這兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In view of all we have to cover today...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}預見到我們今天要做的一切...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I suggest we have a quick look at your apartment and get started.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我建議我們去看看你的住所 馬上去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have the Torrances' things brought to their apartment.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}把特朗斯先生全家的行李 搬到他們的住所去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better collect my family first.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我最好先叫上我的家人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our Colorado Lounge.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這是我們的休閒室{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很漂亮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My God!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is fantastic, isn't it, hon?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這個地方實在太不可思議了 不是嗎 親愛的?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}的確是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anything like this before.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我從來沒見過這樣的東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are all these lndian designs authentic?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那些全部是正統印地安風格嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe they're based...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我相信它們是主要是...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...mainly on Navajo and Apache motifs.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}基於納瓦霍和阿帕契部族的風格{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're really gorgeous.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它們真是非常的華麗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a matter of fact...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}事實上...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is probably the most gorgeous hotel I've ever seen.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這可能是我所見過的最華麗的旅館了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This old place has had an illustrious past.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這個古老的地方有一個輝煌的過去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In its heyday, it was a stopping place for the jet setters...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在全盛時期 乘噴射機旅行的富豪 都當這裏是重要觀光景點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even before anybody knew what a jet set was.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}甚至在噴射客機旅行流行以前{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had four presidents who stayed here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這裏曾經有四位總統呆過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of movie stars.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很多的影視明星{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Royalty?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}皇族呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the best people.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所有最出色的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.38,0:22:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the staff wing of the hotel.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這是旅館職員的宿舍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of the other bedrooms are heated during the winter.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}冬天裏這裏以外的房間都沒有暖氣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Goodbye, Mr. Ullman. - Goodbye, girls.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 再見 尤爾曼先生 - 再見 姑娘們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here are your quarters.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這裏便是你們的居室{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.06,0:22:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Living room, bedroom, bathroom.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}客廳 臥室 浴室{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a small bedroom for your son.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}還有一間小房間 給你的兒子住{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect for a child.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}對孩子而言 這相當不錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then. Place is very nicely self-contained.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯 這裏什麼東西都很齊全{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.19,0:22:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy to keep.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比較好管理{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.53,0:22:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cozy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很舒適{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.80,0:22:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, very cozy for a family.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 對一個家庭而言 非常舒適{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel like spreading out...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}假如你們想繼續的話...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.17,0:23:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you have the rest of the hotel to move around in.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要知道 你們還得去看看其它的那些地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.48,0:23:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's very...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯 這裏非常的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.51,0:23:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...homey.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有家的感覺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our famous hedge maze.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這是我們著名的樹籬迷宮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.19,0:23:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite an attraction here. The walls are 13 feet high...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這是非常有吸引力的所在 牆高是13英尺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.69,0:23:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the hedge is as old as the hotel itself.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}還有這些樹籬 它們就像這個旅館一樣歷史悠久{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of fun, but I wouldn't want to go in there...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}非常有趣 不過 我絕對不想走進去...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.03,0:23:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...unless I had an hour to spare to find my way out.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}除非我自己有把握 一個小時內能走出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.44,0:23:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When was the Overlook built?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}遙望旅館是什麼時候修建的?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Construction started in 1907.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}1907年開始建造{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was finished in 1909.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}1909年竣工{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.15,0:23:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The site's supposed to be on an lndian burial ground.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}地基據說是印地安人的墓地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They actually had to repel...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這一度激怒了他們...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.85,0:23:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a few lndian attacks as they were building it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}甚至在修建過程中 遭遇過印地安人的攻擊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.36,0:23:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Snowcat.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這是我們的雪地車{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.96,0:23:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you both drive a car?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你們兩個都會開吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. Basically the Snowcat operates very much like a car.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好 一般說來 開雪地車就跟開普通車輛沒兩樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.30,0:23:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take you long to get the hang of it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不會花太多時間來掌握它的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:24:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a matter of fact, we brought a decorator in from Chicago...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}事實上 我們曾經從芝加哥找了個漆匠...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.64,0:24:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just last year to refurbish this part of the hotel.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就在去年 重新粉刷旅館的這個部分{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.98,0:24:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure did a beautiful job.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他的確做的非常漂亮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.15,0:24:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pink and gold are my favorite colors.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}粉紅和金色是我最喜歡的色彩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.29,0:24:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our Gold Ballroom.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這是我們的黃金舞廳{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哇塞!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.69,0:24:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can accommodate up to 300 people here very comfortably.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們可以讓300人在這裏舒適地聚會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.00,0:24:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, we could really have a good party in this room.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哈 我們可以在這裏開個精采的派對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.07,0:24:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid you won't do too well here unless you brought supplies.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我恐怕 在你獲得補給品之前 此處也不真能讓你開個好派對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.07,0:24:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We remove the booze from the premises when we shut down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在關閉前 我們會把酒從櫃檯那邊移走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.34,0:24:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reduces the insurance we normally have to carry.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這將減低我們的保險費用{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.61,0:24:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't drink.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們並不喝酒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.78,0:24:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're in luck.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那麼 你們非常幸運{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.42,0:24:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dick, come on over and say hello to Mr. and Mrs. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}迪克 過來跟特朗斯太太和先生問個好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.85,0:24:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Dick Hallorann, our head chef.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這是迪克·哈羅朗 我們的首席廚師{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.19,0:24:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hallorann, I'm Jack. This is my wife, Winifred.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哈羅朗先生 我是傑克 這是我的妻子 溫妮芙瑞德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.13,0:24:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to meet you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很高興認識你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.53,0:24:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Torrances will take care of the Overlook this winter.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}特朗斯一家人 將在這個冬季照顧遙望旅館{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.60,0:24:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just great. How do you folks like our hotel so far?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這很好啊 你們對我們的旅館印象如何?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.54,0:24:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just wonderful.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}非常棒的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.61,0:24:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Danny!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗨 丹尼!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.04,0:25:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found him outside looking for you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我剛好在外面遇上他 他在找你們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.95,0:25:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get tired of bombing the universe?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你已經厭倦玩遊戲了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.22,0:25:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on over here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}到這邊來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.92,0:25:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Susie.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}謝謝你 蘇西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.29,0:25:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be good if you could show Mrs. Torrance the kitchen...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你應該帶特朗斯太太去看一下廚房{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.50,0:25:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...while I continue on with Jack.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我和傑克可以繼續逛逛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.56,0:25:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a pleasure. Right this way.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那是我的榮幸 請這邊走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.20,0:25:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great. See you later, honey.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 一會見 親愛的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.97,0:25:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, darling.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}再見 親愛的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.71,0:25:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Torrance, your husband introduced you as Winifred.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}特朗斯太太 你丈夫介紹你說名字叫溫妮芙瑞德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.24,0:25:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, are you a "Winnie", or a "Freddie"?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那麼 是叫你"溫妮"還是"芙瑞蒂"?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.98,0:25:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Wendy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}叫我溫蒂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.45,0:25:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy. That's nice. That's the prettiest.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}溫蒂 不錯 非常好的稱呼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.85,0:25:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the kitchen, huh?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這裏就是廚房嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.69,0:25:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.49,0:25:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like it, Danny? is it big enough for you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你喜歡這裏嗎 丹尼? 對你而言 這裏夠大了嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.26,0:25:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the biggest place I ever seen.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這是我見過的最大的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.70,0:25:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This whole place is such an enormous maze.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這整個地方就像個巨大的迷宮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.23,0:25:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to leave a trail of breadcrumbs every time I come in.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我每次進來都得撒些麵包屑做標記{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.71,0:25:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it get you down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要讓它把你嚇倒了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.78,0:25:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's big, but it ain't nothing but a kitchen.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它是很大 不過無論怎樣也只是間廚房而已{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.48,0:25:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of this stuff you'll never have to touch.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這裏許多東西你都沒必要去碰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.88,0:26:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know what to do with it if I did.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果亂碰 我將很難收拾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.32,0:26:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One thing for sure, you don't have to worry about food.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有一件事是肯定的 你不要擔心沒有食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.65,0:26:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You folks could eat here for a year and never have the same menu twice.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}足夠你們在這兒吃一年 而且保證每次的菜單都不一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.53,0:26:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here is our walk-in freezer.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這裏是我們的冷藏室{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.76,0:26:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we keep all of our meat.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們在這裏存放肉類{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.04,0:26:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got 15 rib roasts...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這裏有15塊烘乾的排骨...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.24,0:26:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...30 ten-pound bags of hamburger.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}30袋漢堡 每袋10磅...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.57,0:26:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got 12 turkeys, about 40 chickens...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}還有12只火雞 大約40隻雞...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.84,0:26:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...50 sirloin steaks, two dozen of pork roast...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}50份牛排 2打豬排...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.15,0:26:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and 20 legs of lamb. Do you like lamb, Doc?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}還有20條羔羊腿 你喜歡羔羊吧 多克?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.35,0:26:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't? What's your favorite food, then?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不喜歡? 那 你最喜歡的是什麼食物呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.92,0:26:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,French fries and ketchup.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}法國油炸食物和調味醬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.53,0:26:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can manage that too, Doc.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想我們也能找到那個的 多克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.73,0:26:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come along, now. Watch your step.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}繼續走 小心你們的腳下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.21,0:26:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you know we call him Doc?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你怎麼知道我們叫他多克?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.97,0:26:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Beg your pardon? - Doc. You called Danny "Doc" twice.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你什麼意思? - 多克 你叫了丹尼兩次"多克"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.21,0:26:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我有嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.42,0:27:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We call him Doc sometimes, like in the Bugs Bunny cartoons.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們有時叫他多克 就像卡通片 "瘋狂的兔子" 裏一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.75,0:27:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you know?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是 你是怎麼知道的呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.22,0:27:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I probably heard you call him that.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想 我可能是聽到你這麼叫他了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.96,0:27:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible. But I honestly don't remember...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有可能 但是我真的不記得...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.43,0:27:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...calling him that since we've been with you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在我們見面後我有這麼叫過他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.83,0:27:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, he looks like a Doc, doesn't he?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}無論如何 他看起來就像是多克 不是麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.47,0:27:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Doc?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎麼了 多克?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.74,0:27:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this is the storeroom.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯 這裏是儲藏室{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.68,0:27:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In here is where we keep...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在這裏我們存放...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.71,0:27:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all the dried goods and the canned goods.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所有的干料和罐頭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.71,0:27:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got canned fruits and vegetables...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們有罐裝的水果和蔬菜...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.35,0:27:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...canned fish and meats, hot and cold cereals.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}罐裝的魚和肉食 還有其它一些糧食{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.36,0:27:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Post Toasties, Corn Flakes, Sugar Puffs...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比如麵包片 薯片 甜點...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.76,0:27:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rice Krispies, oatmeal, Wheatena and Cream of Wheat.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}爆米花 麥片 還有小麥油{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.03,0:27:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a dozen jugs of black molasses.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}還有成打的黑楓糖...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.67,0:27:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got 60 boxes of dried milk...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}60箱牛奶...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.51,0:27:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like some ice cream, Doc?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你想要些冰淇淋嗎 多克?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.39,0:28:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sociables, finger rolls...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}各種小吃 甜點...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.59,0:28:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and 7 kinds of what have you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你想要的每種食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.32,0:28:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we've got dried peaches, dried apricots...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯 我們有桃干 杏干...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.06,0:28:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...dried raisins and dried prunes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}...葡萄乾和李干{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.36,0:28:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you got to keep regular if you want to be happy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道 如果你想快樂一點 你必須要保持秩序{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.57,0:28:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- How're you getting on? - Fine.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你們進行得怎樣? - 很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.41,0:28:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we borrow Mrs. Torrance? We're on our way to the basement.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}能借用一下特朗斯太太嗎? 我們正打算去地下室{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.18,0:28:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise we won't keep her very long.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我保證不會佔用很長時間的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.32,0:28:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem, Mr.Ullman. I was just getting to the ice cream.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 尤爾曼先生 我正打算去做冰淇淋的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.72,0:28:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like ice cream, Doc?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你喜歡冰淇淋吧 多克?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.46,0:28:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you did.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我認為你喜歡呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.62,0:28:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You folks mind if I give Danny some ice cream while we wait?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你們介意在等你們的這段時間 我給丹尼一些冰淇淋麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.89,0:28:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Not at all. - We don't mind.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 當然不會 - 我們不介意的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.93,0:28:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good. - Sound good to you, Doc?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 好的 - 聽到這個你很高興吧 多克?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.33,0:28:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you behave yourself.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好吧 你們去做你們的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.41,0:28:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of ice cream do you like?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你想要哪種冰淇淋呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.48,0:28:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}巧克力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.58,0:28:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate it shall be. Come on, son.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那就是巧克力的 來吧 孩子 過來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.12,0:28:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing, all this activity today.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}今天真是非常神奇的一天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.32,0:29:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guests and some staff left yesterday, but the...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}客人和部分職員昨天就走了 但是...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.33,0:29:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...last day's always hectic.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這最後一天仍然是令人興奮的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.96,0:29:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody wants to be on their way as early as possible.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}每個人都想盡早上路{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.23,0:29:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By 5:00 tonight, you'll never know anybody was ever here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}今晚5點後 就很難想像 這個地方有很多人在的樣子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.47,0:29:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like a ghost ship, huh?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就像艘鬼船一樣 不是嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.21,0:29:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how I knew your name was Doc?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你曉得為什麼 我知道你的名字叫多克嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.76,0:29:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I'm talking about, don't you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不明白我在說什麼吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.13,0:29:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can remember when I was a little boy...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我記得 在我還小的時候...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.04,0:29:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my grandmother and I could hold conversations...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}...我的祖母和我可以...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.77,0:29:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...entirely without ever opening our mouths.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}...完全不開口進行交談{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.68,0:29:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She called it "shining."\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她管這叫"閃靈"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.48,0:29:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for a long time I thought it was just the two of us...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一直以來 我都認為只有我和她...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.42,0:29:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that had "the shine" to us.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}擁有"閃靈"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.66,0:30:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you probably thought you was the only one.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就像你也可能 一直認為自己有獨特天賦一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.33,0:30:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are other folks...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是 還有其他人也是一樣的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.40,0:30:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...though mostly they don't know it, or don't believe it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}雖然他們大多數都沒有體會到 甚至不相信{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.81,0:30:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been able to do it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你能這樣已經多久了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.45,0:30:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you want to talk about it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你為什麼不想談談它呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.09,0:30:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not supposed to.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不該那樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.73,0:30:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who says you ain't supposed to?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}誰說你不該那樣?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.70,0:30:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tony.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}托尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.07,0:30:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Tony?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}誰是托尼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.21,0:30:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tony's the little boy that lives in my mouth.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}托尼是住在我嘴裏的小男孩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.55,0:30:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Tony the one that...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}托尼就是那個...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.79,0:30:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...tells you things?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}告訴你古怪事情的人?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.90,0:31:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does he tell you things?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他怎樣告訴你的?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.10,0:31:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I go to sleep, and he shows me things.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我就像是睡著了一樣 然後 他就給我看一些東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.61,0:31:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I wake up, I can't remember everything.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是 當我醒來後 我就記不起來發生了什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.55,0:31:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does your mom and dad know about Tony?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你父母知道托尼的事嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.75,0:31:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes. - Do they know he tells you things?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 他們知道 - 托尼有告訴你奇怪的事情嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.99,0:31:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Tony told me never to tell them.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不知道 托尼叫我絕對不要和他們說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.06,0:31:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Tony ever told you anything about this place?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}托尼有告訴過你這個地方的事嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.63,0:31:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Overlook Hotel?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}關於遙望旅館?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.47,0:31:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.94,0:31:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now think real hard, Doc.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}仔細想想 多克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.95,0:31:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}想想{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.09,0:31:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he showed me something.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他似乎有給我看過一些東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.76,0:31:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to think of what it was.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那 仔細想想是什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.40,0:31:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hallorann, are you scared of this place?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哈羅朗先生 你害怕這個地方嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.80,0:32:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Scared of nothing here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不怕 並不害怕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.51,0:32:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只是...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.74,0:32:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you know, some places are like people.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道的 一些地方 似乎就像人一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.41,0:32:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some shine...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有的很特別...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.32,0:32:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and some don't.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但 有的卻相反{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.95,0:32:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say the Overlook Hotel...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想遙望旅館...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.29,0:32:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has something about it that's like shining.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它有些東西 很特別 就像閃靈一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.63,0:32:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something bad here?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這裏有發生過不好的事嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.65,0:32:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Doc, when something happens...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道 多克 一些事發生後...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.28,0:32:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it can leave a trace of itself behind.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它總會留下一些痕跡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.69,0:32:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, like...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯 就像...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.46,0:32:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if someone burns toast.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}大鬍子會在鬍鬚上留下麵包屑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.63,0:32:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe things that happen leave other kind of traces behind.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是 某些事情卻留下不一樣的痕跡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.47,0:33:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not things that anyone can notice.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是所有人都可以注意到的那種痕跡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.11,0:33:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But things that people who shine can see.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是 擁有閃靈的人可以看到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.01,0:33:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like they can see things that haven't happened yet...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就像他們能看到還沒發生的事一樣...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.59,0:33:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sometimes they can see things that happened a long time ago.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在某些時候 他們能看到許久以前發生的一些事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.29,0:33:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think a lot of things happened right here...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想 這裏曾經發生過許多事...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.36,0:33:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in this particular hotel over the years.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在這所特別的旅館的悠久歷史裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.60,0:33:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And not all of them was good.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這些事 並不全都是好事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.31,0:33:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about room 237?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那麼 237房發生過什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.28,0:33:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 237?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}237房?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.79,0:33:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scared of room 237, ain't you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你害怕237房 不是嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.66,0:33:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I ain't.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不怕 我不害怕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.63,0:33:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hallorann, what is in room 237?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哈羅朗先生 237房裏面到底有些什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.80,0:33:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什麼也沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.60,0:33:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There ain't nothing in room 237.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}237房裏面沒有什麼 根本沒有!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.04,0:34:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you ain't got no business going in there anyway.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而且 你也沒有必要去那個地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.48,0:34:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So stay out.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所以 不要靠近它{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.81,0:34:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand? Stay out!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}明白了嗎? 不要靠近它!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.16,0:34:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一個月後{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.70,0:35:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, hon.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}早晨 親愛的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.44,0:35:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your breakfast is ready.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的早餐已經做好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.97,0:35:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}現在幾點?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.81,0:35:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about 11:30.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}大概11點30分{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.58,0:36:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.12,0:36:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we've been staying up too late.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想我們實在是睡得太晚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.85,0:36:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.59,0:36:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made them just the way you like them, sunny-side up.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}都按你喜歡的口味做的 嘗嘗吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.76,0:36:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.60,0:36:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really pretty outside.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}外面的風景真的很美{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.60,0:36:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about taking me for a walk after you finish your breakfast?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}吃完早餐後 我們可以出去散步麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.44,0:36:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I ought to try to do some writing first.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想我得先寫些東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.21,0:36:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any ideas yet?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有什麼構思了嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.88,0:36:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of ideas.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}太多的構思{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.75,0:36:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good ones.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是都沒有好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.75,0:36:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something will come.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好創意總會有的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.72,0:36:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a matter of settling into the habit of writing every day.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}關鍵是要養成每天都得寫作的習慣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.23,0:36:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all it is.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就是這樣而已{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.03,0:36:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really nice up here, isn't it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}到這個地方來真是不錯啊 不是嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.74,0:36:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我喜歡這兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.67,0:36:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really do.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真的喜歡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.18,0:36:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been this happy or comfortable anywhere.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我從來沒有在別的地方 感覺有這麼舒適和快活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.41,0:36:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing how fast you get used to such a big place.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你這麼快就能適應這樣一個大地方 真是讓人驚訝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.38,0:37:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tell you, when we first came up here...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}老實說 我們剛來的時候...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.49,0:37:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I thought it was kind of scary.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我認為這裏會非常可怕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.99,0:37:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell in love with it right away.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是我立刻就喜歡上了這兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.23,0:37:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I came up here for my interview...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}當我來這裏應聘的時候...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.40,0:37:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it was as though I'd been here before.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就感到 我似乎曾經來過這兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.44,0:37:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we all have moments of deja vu...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的意思是 我們總會有些似曾相識的感覺...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.27,0:37:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but this was ridiculous.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是這次有些不一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.21,0:37:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was almost as though I knew...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我幾乎能知道...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.88,0:37:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what was going to be around every corner.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}每個角落會有些什麼東西存在{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.15,0:38:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The loser has to keep America clean. How's that?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}輸了的人就要打掃整個美國 怎樣?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.56,0:38:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- All right. - And you're going to lose.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 好的 - 你已經要輸了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.33,0:38:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to get you. You'd better run fast!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要來抓你了 你最好跑快點!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.47,0:38:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}注意了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.81,0:38:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in close.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我快抓到你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.88,0:38:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loser has to keep America clean.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}輸家要打掃整個美國哦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.61,0:38:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep America clean.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要打掃整個美國{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.25,0:38:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Danny, you win.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}丹尼 你贏了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.05,0:38:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take the rest of this walking.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們休息會吧 走走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.92,0:38:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your hand.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}把手給我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.96,0:38:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it beautiful?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這裏很漂亮吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.52,0:38:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead end.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}死胡同{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.35,0:39:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.49,0:39:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it beautiful?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很漂亮吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.42,0:40:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}非常漂亮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.82,0:40:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think it was going to be this big. Did you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我沒有想到它居然這麼大 你呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.03,0:40:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.73,0:40:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}星期二{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.37,0:40:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rutherford was serving a life sentence...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}盧瑟福在追查一起...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.97,0:40:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for a 1968 shooting.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在1968年執行槍決的命案{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.94,0:40:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the search continues for that missing Aspen woman.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}對在阿斯本失蹤婦女的搜索 仍然持續進行著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.02,0:40:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,24-year-old Susan Robertson has been missing 10 days.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}蘇珊·羅伯遜 24歲 已經失蹤10天了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.59,0:40:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She disappeared on a hunting trip with her husband.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她在和丈夫一起的打獵途中走失{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.52,0:40:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They may have to call off the search...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他們也許不得不取消搜索...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.53,0:40:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if a predicted snowstorm moves in tomorrow.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}假如預測的暴風雪明天果真來臨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.26,0:41:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful in Denver today...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}丹佛今天風和日麗...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.33,0:41:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's hard to believe a snowstorm could be close.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很難想像一場暴風雪就要來臨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.67,0:41:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go outside and lie in the sun...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我甚至想出去沐浴陽光...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.10,0:41:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...yet to our north, to our west, it is snowing and cold.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在我們的北方和西方 天氣仍然很冷 下著雪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.44,0:41:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's moving...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而且冷空氣在移動...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.84,0:41:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...right here towards Colorado as we talk. It's incredible.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這同時 它正移向科羅拉多州 難以置信...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.56,0:43:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, honey.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗨 親愛的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.59,0:43:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}工作進行得怎樣?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.57,0:43:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}還行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.84,0:43:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a lot written today?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}今天寫了很多嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.10,0:44:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.45,0:44:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather forecast said it's going to snow tonight.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天氣預報說 今晚會開始下雪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.22,0:44:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do about it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那又怎樣? 你想我怎樣?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.69,0:44:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, honey.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好了 親愛的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.20,0:44:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so grouchy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不用這麼不高興吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.63,0:44:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我並沒有...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.33,0:44:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...being grouchy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不高興{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.74,0:44:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to finish my work.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我只是想完成我的工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.04,0:44:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I understand.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 我明白了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.68,0:44:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back later with a couple of sandwiches.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一會兒我給你帶點三明治來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.48,0:44:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you'll let me read something then.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}到那時候 你也許能讓我看看 你已經寫了些什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.16,0:44:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}溫蒂...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.46,0:44:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...let me explain something to you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}...讓我告訴你一件事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.96,0:44:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you come in and interrupt, you're breaking my concentration.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}當你進來打斷我的時候 意味著你破壞了我的集中力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.03,0:44:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're distracting me...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你把我的注意力轉移開了...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.67,0:44:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it will then take me time to get back to where I was.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我得費力氣 再把注意力擺回工作上去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.31,0:44:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}明白了嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.63,0:45:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}明白{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.01,0:45:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.35,0:45:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to make a new rule:\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們得定個新規矩:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.28,0:45:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I'm in here...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}無論什麼時候 只要我在這裏...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.92,0:45:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you hear me typing...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你有聽到我打字的聲音...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.99,0:45:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or whatever the fuck you hear me doing in here...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或者 無論你聽到我在這裏幹什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.13,0:45:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when I'm in here, that means I am working.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只要我呆在這兒 就意味著我在工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.63,0:45:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means don't come in.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}也就是說 那時不能進來打擾我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.07,0:45:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, do you think you can handle that?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好了 你現在明白了嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.58,0:45:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah. - Fine.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 嗯 - 好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.14,0:45:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you start right now and get the fuck out of here?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那你怎麼還不行動 給我滾出這個地方?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.82,0:45:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.73,0:46:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}星期四{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.39,0:46:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你好了吧!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.19,0:46:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you've got more.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道你手裏面還有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.10,0:46:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Missed!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}沒打中!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.74,0:46:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't have!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}現在沒了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.81,0:46:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair anymore.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那不怕你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.40,0:46:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}星期六{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.72,0:47:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我應該早想到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.29,0:48:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is KDK 12 calling KDK 1.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這是KDK 12在呼叫KDK 1{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.30,0:48:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KDK 12 to KDK 1.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}KDK 12 呼叫 KDK 1{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.20,0:48:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is KDK 1. We're receiving you. Over.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這邊是KDK 1 我們收到你的呼叫了 完畢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.71,0:48:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, this is Wendy Torrance at the Overlook Hotel.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗨 我是遙望旅館的溫蒂·特朗斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.41,0:48:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, how are you folks getting on up there? Over.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗨 你們在上頭過得如何? 完畢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.48,0:48:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just fine.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們過得很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.02,0:48:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But our telephones aren't doing too well.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是我們的電話 似乎有點問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.69,0:48:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the lines down, by any chance? Over.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是線路斷了嗎? 完畢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.36,0:48:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, quite a few of them are down due to the storm. Over.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 因為暴風雪的關係 一部分線路出問題了 完畢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.46,0:48:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any chance of them being repaired soon? Over.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有可能盡快修好嗎? 完畢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.87,0:48:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wouldn't like to say.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯 我恐怕不行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.23,0:48:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most winters they stay that way until spring. Over.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可能整個冬天都只能這樣 得等到春天才會修理 完畢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.17,0:48:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, this storm is really something, isn't it? Over.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}夥計 這暴風雪可真是厲害 不是嗎? 完畢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.04,0:48:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's one of the worst we've had for years.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 真是如此{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.51,0:48:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else we can do for you, Mrs. Torrance?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們還能為你做點其它的什麼嗎? 特朗斯太太 完畢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.19,0:48:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose not. Over.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想 沒什麼了 完畢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.95,0:49:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you folks have any problems up there, just give us a call.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}假如你們遇到什麼麻煩 就呼叫我們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.46,0:49:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, Mrs. Torrance?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}還有 特朗斯太太...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.96,0:49:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be a good idea if you leave your radio on all the time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你們最好一直都開著無線通話裝置{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.00,0:49:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. We'll do that.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 我們會這樣做的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.70,0:49:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was real nice talking to you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很高興能和你交談{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.97,0:49:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye. Over and out.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}再見 掛斷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.52,0:49:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Danny.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你好 丹尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.99,0:49:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and play with us.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}來和我們一起玩吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.30,0:50:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and play with us, Danny.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}和我們一起玩吧 丹尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.90,0:50:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}永遠...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.54,0:50:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and ever...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}永遠...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.25,0:50:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and ever.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}永遠{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.75,0:50:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tony...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}托尼...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.39,0:50:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm scared.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我很害怕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.90,0:51:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what Mr. Hallorann said.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}記住哈羅朗先生說過的話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.07,0:51:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like pictures in a book, Danny.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那就像是書裏的插畫一樣 沒什麼好怕的 丹尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.17,0:51:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't real.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那並不是真實的東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.27,0:51:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}星期一{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.51,0:51:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me give you some money.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}請讓我給你些錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.54,0:51:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't think of it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要 我想我不能接受{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.81,0:51:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how can I repay you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 那你要我怎樣報答你?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.04,0:51:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Really.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不用了 真的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.58,0:51:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going to have some coffee.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯 我想喝些咖啡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.88,0:51:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你也喝點好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.15,0:51:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.42,0:51:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great. Sit down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好 請坐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.20,0:51:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marvelous doughnuts. Help yourself.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}神奇炸圈餅 你自己拿罷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.48,0:51:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Coffee will be ready in a few minutes. - Mom.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 咖啡馬上就好 - 媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.96,0:51:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.68,0:52:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go up to my room and get my fire engine?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我能去我的房間拿我的消防車嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.45,0:52:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not right now. Daddy's asleep.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}現在不行 爸爸正在睡覺呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.16,0:52:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make any noise.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我會小心不出聲的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.73,0:52:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now come on, Doc.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯 多克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.83,0:52:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He only went to bed a few hours ago.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你爸爸才睡了一會兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.74,0:52:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you wait till later?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不能再等等麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.74,0:52:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make a sound. I promise I'll tiptoe.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不會弄出聲響的 我保證 我會掂腳尖走進去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.08,0:52:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.58,0:52:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But really don't make a sound.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是真的不要弄出聲音{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.18,0:52:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't, Mom.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不會的 媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.48,0:52:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you come right back...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拿到就馬上回來...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.42,0:52:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I'm going to make lunch soon.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因為我得馬上去做午飯了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.56,0:52:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Mom.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.32,0:53:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go to my room and get my fire engine?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我能去我的房間拿我的消防車嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.23,0:53:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here for a minute first.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}到這邊來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.44,0:54:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going, Doc?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}感覺怎樣呢 多克?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.70,0:54:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.81,0:54:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having a good time?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}過得好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.68,0:54:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Dad.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 爸爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.06,0:54:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.49,0:54:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to have a good time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我希望你能過得愉快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.36,0:54:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am, Dad.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我很愉快 爸爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.54,0:54:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Dad. - yes?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 爸爸 - 什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.44,0:54:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel bad?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你感覺不好?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.39,0:54:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm just a little bit tired.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是 只是有些累{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.06,0:55:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you go to sleep?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那 你為什麼不睡會呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.20,0:55:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不能睡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.23,0:55:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got too much to do.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因為還有很多事得做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.85,0:55:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like this hotel?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你喜歡這所旅館嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.12,0:55:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.49,0:55:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我喜歡它{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.03,0:55:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}難道你不是嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.74,0:55:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想 我也是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.87,0:55:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.28,0:55:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to like it here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我希望你能喜歡這裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.59,0:55:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could stay here forever...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我希望我們能永遠待在這個地方...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.19,0:55:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and ever...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}永遠...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.66,0:55:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and ever.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}永遠{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.44,0:56:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.74,0:56:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would never hurt Mommy or me, would you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你永遠都不會傷害我和媽媽 對嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.31,0:56:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你什麼意思?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.92,0:56:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your mother ever say that to you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你媽媽對你說過些什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.19,0:56:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I would hurt you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}說我會傷害你?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.76,0:56:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Dad.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}沒有 爸爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.30,0:56:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你確定?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.40,0:56:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Dad.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 爸爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.78,0:56:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Danny.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我愛你 丹尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.01,0:56:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you more than anything else...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我愛你 勝過一切...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.82,0:56:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the whole world...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}勝過世上的任何東西...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.15,0:56:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I would never do anything to hurt you...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我永遠不會傷害你的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.52,0:56:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...never.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}永遠{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.63,0:56:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that, don't you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道的 不是嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.16,0:56:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Dad.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 爸爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.67,0:57:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.49,0:57:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}星期三{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.50,0:57:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.69,0:58:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.70,0:58:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, are you in there?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}媽媽 你在嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.73,0:59:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎麼了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.00,0:59:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}親愛的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.10,0:59:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what's wrong?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}發生了什麼事?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.68,1:00:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had the most...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我作夢了...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.28,1:00:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...terrible nightmare I ever had.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}作一個我一生中最可怕的夢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.82,1:00:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- It was the most horrible dream. - It's okay, it's okay now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 最最可怕的 - 好了 好了 現在沒事了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.96,1:00:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真的?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.60,1:00:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamed that I...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我夢見...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.40,1:00:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I killed you and Danny.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我殺了你和丹尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.57,1:00:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't just kill you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是 我不僅僅是殺了你們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.11,1:00:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cut you up into little pieces.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我還把你們切成一片一片的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.55,1:00:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My God.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.79,1:00:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be losing my mind.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我一定是瘋了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.62,1:00:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's going to be all right.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一切都會沒事的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.36,1:00:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's get up off the floor.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 讓我們站起來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.91,1:00:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There. Now sit up.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}坐下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.85,1:01:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.25,1:01:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}放鬆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.76,1:01:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Danny!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}丹尼!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.26,1:01:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's okay!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}沒什麼事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.39,1:01:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go play in your room for a while.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}去你的房間玩會兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.90,1:01:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad's just got a headache.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你爸爸有些頭痛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.27,1:01:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Danny, mind what I say. Go play in your room.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}丹尼 聽到我說什麼了嗎? 去你房間裏玩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.27,1:01:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, let me just go get him out of here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}親愛的 等我把他帶走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.41,1:01:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我馬上就回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.85,1:01:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you mind me?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你為什麼不聽我的話?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.52,1:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哦 天啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.56,1:01:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your neck?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你脖子上是怎麼搞的?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.90,1:01:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your neck?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你脖子上到底是怎麼回事?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.00,1:02:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did this to him...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你對他這樣的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.40,1:02:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...didn't you?!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是你嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.67,1:02:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你這個狗娘養的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.94,1:02:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did this to him!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你居然這樣對他!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.01,1:02:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you?!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你居然? !{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.78,1:02:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you?!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你怎麼可以這樣? !{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.69,1:02:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you?!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你怎麼忍心? !{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.29,1:04:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God! I'd give anything for a drink.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我得來點喝的 無論要我付出什麼代價{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.03,1:04:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd give my goddamn soul...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}即便付出我該死的靈魂...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.14,1:04:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for just a glass of beer.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}能換來一杯啤酒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.62,1:04:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Lloyd.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗨 羅伊德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.66,1:04:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little slow tonight, isn't it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}今晚似乎沒什麼人 不是嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.94,1:04:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes it is, Mr. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 特朗斯先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.28,1:04:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will it be?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}想要點什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.41,1:04:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm awfully glad you asked me that, Lloyd...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這個問題你問得好 羅伊德...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.58,1:04:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I just happen to have two twenties...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因為我正好有兩張20塊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.12,1:04:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and two tens right here in my wallet.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}和兩張10塊的鈔票擺在我口袋裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.22,1:05:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid they were going to be there until next April.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我正擔心 它們會在口袋裏待到下個春天呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.20,1:05:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So here's what:\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好 聽著 我要的是:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.33,1:05:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You slip me a bottle of bourbon...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你給我一瓶波本...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.84,1:05:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a little glass and some ice.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}和一個裝了冰塊的杯子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.84,1:05:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do that, can't you, Lloyd?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你能做到吧 不是嗎 羅伊德?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.31,1:05:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not too busy, are you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你並不很忙 是吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.25,1:05:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir. I'm not busy at all.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 先生 我一點都不忙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.25,1:05:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good man.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好夥計{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.12,1:05:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You set them up...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你把它們擺好...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.49,1:05:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I'll knock them back, one by one.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我會把它們各個擊破{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.49,1:05:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White man's burden, Lloyd, my man.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}白人的使命 羅伊德 我的夥計{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.63,1:05:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White man's burden.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}白人的使命 (暗指: 擊退印地安人){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.87,1:05:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Lloyd...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我說 羅伊德...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.21,1:05:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it seems I'm temporarily light.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我好像一時有點輕飄飄了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.31,1:05:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's my credit in this joint, anyway?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不管怎麼說 我在這邊信譽如何?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.01,1:05:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your credit's fine, Mr. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的信譽很好 特朗斯先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.08,1:05:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's swell.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我可以發誓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.92,1:05:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you, Lloyd.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我欣賞你 羅伊德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.82,1:05:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always liked you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我一直都欣賞你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.69,1:05:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were always the best of them.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是其中最優秀的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.23,1:05:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Best goddamned bartender...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好得不能再好的吧檯招待...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.79,1:06:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from Timbuktu to Portland, Maine.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}從蒂姆布克圖到緬因州的波特蘭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.93,1:06:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or Portland, Oregon, for that matter.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或是到俄勒岡州的波特蘭 都是一樣的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.43,1:06:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saying so.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}謝謝誇獎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.54,1:06:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's to 5 miserable months on the wagon...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在貨車上過了備受煎熬的5個月...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.28,1:06:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and all the irreparable harm that it's caused me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}給我帶來了永久的心靈創傷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.57,1:06:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are things going, Mr. Torrance?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}過得還順利吧? 特朗斯先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.38,1:06:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things could be better.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}情況會好轉的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.48,1:06:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things could be a whole lot better.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}情況會整個徹底好轉的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.12,1:06:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it's nothing serious.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我希望沒什麼太大問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.46,1:06:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing serious.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}沒什麼大問題啦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.09,1:07:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little problem with...the old sperm bank upstairs.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只是跟樓上的哪個老精子銀行(注:溫蒂) 有點小小問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.20,1:07:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing I can't handle, though.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但我完全可以掌握{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.77,1:07:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.94,1:07:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Women.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}女人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.14,1:07:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't live with them...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不能夠和她們一起生活...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.88,1:07:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't live without them.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}離開她們又活不下去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.92,1:07:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Words of wisdom, Lloyd.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}智慧金言 羅伊德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.69,1:07:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Words of...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}智慧...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.35,1:07:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wisdom.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}良言{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.40,1:07:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never laid a hand on him, goddamn it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我絕沒有碰他 媽的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.84,1:07:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.51,1:07:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't touch one hair on his goddamn little head.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}連一根寒毛都沒去碰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.72,1:07:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love the little son of a bitch.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我愛那個小王八蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.46,1:07:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd do anything for him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我會為他做任何事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.49,1:07:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any fucking thing for him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他媽的任何事情{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.37,1:08:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that bitch!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但那個婊子!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.94,1:08:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I live...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只要我還活著...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.91,1:08:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she'll never let me forget what happened.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她就不會讓我忘記發生過的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.92,1:08:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did hurt him once, okay?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我確實傷害過他一次 好不好?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.13,1:08:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an accident.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}單純的意外{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.50,1:08:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Completely unintentional.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}完全不算故意的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.37,1:08:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could have happened to anybody.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}任何人遇到那種事 都可能那樣反應{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.34,1:08:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was three goddamn years ago!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而且 他媽的 都過去三個年頭了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.01,1:08:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The little fucker had thrown all my papers all over the floor.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那小雜碎把我的稿紙扔滿地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.05,1:08:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I tried to do was pull him up.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我只是想把他拉起來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.29,1:08:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A momentary loss of muscular coordination.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一時肌肉動作失去協調{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.29,1:08:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是說...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.06,1:08:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a few extra foot-pounds of energy...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}力道多出幾磅...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.80,1:08:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...per second, per second.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}平均每秒 每秒才...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.75,1:09:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God you're here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}感謝上帝你在這裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.89,1:09:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone else in the hotel with us.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}旅館裏除了我們 還有另一個人在{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.30,1:09:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a crazy woman in one of the rooms.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}其中一間房子裏有個瘋女人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.03,1:09:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She tried to strangle Danny.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她想把丹尼掐死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.14,1:09:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out of your fucking mind?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你他媽的神智不清了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.48,1:09:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth! Really.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那是真的 真的!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.71,1:09:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear it. Danny told me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我發誓 丹尼告訴我的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.05,1:09:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went up into one of the bedrooms.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他上去 進入其中一間臥房{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.12,1:09:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door was open, and he saw this crazy woman in the bathtub.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}門是開著的 他看見這瘋女人在浴缸裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.79,1:09:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She tried to strangle him!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她想把他掐死!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.83,1:09:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which room was it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在哪個房間?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.24,1:09:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Channel 10 in Miami...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}來自邁阿密的10頻道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.58,1:10:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is Newswatch with Glen Rinker...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這裏是新聞觀察和格蘭林克...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.15,1:10:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Ann Bishop, and the award- winning Newswatch team.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}安畢雪與廣受好評的新聞觀察小組{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.68,1:10:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. I'm Glen Rinker, Newswatch Ten.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}晚安 我是10頻道新聞觀察的格蘭林克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.32,1:10:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Miami continues to swelter in a record winter heat wave...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}當邁阿密悶熱的天氣持續刷新記錄 冬季的熱浪...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.66,1:10:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...bringing temperatures to the 90s...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}帶來超過華氏90度的高溫...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.99,1:10:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Central and Mountain states are buried in snow.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}中部和山區的州區 卻被埋在皚皚白雪之中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.33,1:10:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Colorado, 10 inches of snow fell injust a few hours tonight.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}今晚光是科羅拉多 幾個小時內就積了10英吋厚的雪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.54,1:10:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel in the Rockies is almost impossible.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}幾乎不可能在洛磯山脈從事旅遊活動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.97,1:10:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Airports are shut down, stranding thousands of passengers.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}機場被迫關閉 滯留了成千上萬的旅客{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.14,1:10:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Highways are blocked by snowdrifts.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}高速公路被雪堆阻擋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.24,1:10:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Railroad tracks are frozen.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}鐵軌被凍住{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.21,1:10:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Officials in Colorado tell Newswatch...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}科羅拉多官方告知新聞觀察...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.45,1:10:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at least 3 have been killed by exposure to freezing winds.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}已經至少有三個人在寒風中被凍死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.22,1:10:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The governor of Colorado is expected...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}希望科羅拉多政府...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.72,1:10:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to declare a weather emergency.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}宣佈進入天氣警戒狀態{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.66,1:10:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The National Guard might be called out...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}應動員全民進行防備...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.70,1:10:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to clear streets and roads.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}清除街道和公路積雪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.10,1:10:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weather forecasters predict more snow...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天氣預報 今晚到明天...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.53,1:10:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and heavy winds tonight and tomorrow...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}將有更多的降雪 並伴有強風...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.74,1:10:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with temperatures dropping well below zero.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}同時溫度會降到0度以下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.57,1:10:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back here in Florida, we've got the opposite problem.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}回到佛羅里達 我們碰到了相反的問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.78,1:10:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heat and humidity are supposed to climb.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}炎熱和潮濕預計會更加惡化{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.21,1:11:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Local beaches should bejammed.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}應該封鎖本地的沙灘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.38,1:11:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our weather expert, Walter Cronice...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們的氣象專家華特克朗斯...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.62,1:11:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will have the local forecast later on Newswatch.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}將在稍後的新聞觀察裏 為您播報本地天氣預報{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.57,1:16:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry. Your call cannot be completed as dialed.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}對不起 您所撥的號碼無法接通{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.55,1:16:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need assistance, please call the operator.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果您需要幫助請撥叫接線員{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.64,1:17:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Jack? - Yes, it's me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 傑克? - 是 是我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.97,1:17:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}感謝上帝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.08,1:17:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find anything?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你找到什麼了嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.05,1:17:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Nothing at all.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}沒有 什麼也沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.39,1:17:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see one goddamn thing.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我什麼見鬼的東西都沒看到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.29,1:17:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went into the room Danny said? To 237?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你去了丹尼說的那間房了嗎? 去237?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.00,1:17:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I did.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 我去了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.03,1:17:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you didn't see anything at all?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你什麼也沒看到?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.04,1:17:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely nothing.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}絕對沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.24,1:17:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is he?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他怎麼樣了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.71,1:17:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still asleep.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他還在睡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.91,1:17:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.85,1:17:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll be himself again in the morning.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我肯定明天早上 他就會回過神來的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.43,1:17:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it was the right room?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你確定就是那個房間嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.13,1:17:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, maybe Danny made a mistake.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是說 也許丹尼弄錯了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.50,1:17:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have gone in that room.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他一定就是進去那個房間{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.07,1:18:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door was open, the lights were on.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}門開著 燈也亮著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.38,1:18:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't understand it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我只是弄不明白{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.05,1:18:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about those bruises on his neck?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他脖子上的傷痕是怎麼回事?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.26,1:18:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody did that to him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有人把他弄成那樣的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.87,1:18:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想是...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.97,1:18:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he did it to himself.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他自己弄的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.55,1:18:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不可能{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.45,1:18:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那不可能{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.79,1:18:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you rule out his version of what happened...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一旦你排除他對所發生的事情的說法...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.70,1:18:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there is no other explanation.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就再沒有其他解釋了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.77,1:18:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.47,1:19:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be that different from the episode...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那和我們來這裏前的那次事件...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.58,1:19:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that he had before we came up here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}沒有什麼不同的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.15,1:19:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.29,1:19:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the explanation is...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不管是什麼原因...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.73,1:19:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think we...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想我們...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.33,1:19:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have to get Danny out of here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}得帶丹尼離開這裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.84,1:19:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him out of here?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}帶他離開這裏?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.85,1:19:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的意思是...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.62,1:19:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just leave the hotel?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}離開這座旅館?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.57,1:19:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is so...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}製造一個像這樣的問題...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.23,1:19:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...typical of you to create a problem like this...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這正是你的風格{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.87,1:19:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when I finally have a chance to accomplish something!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}當我總算有機會完成什麼的時候!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.61,1:20:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm really into my work!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}當我真正投入我的作品的時候!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.38,1:20:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could really write my own ticket if I went back now, couldn't I?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果現在回去 我真的能寫出自己的大作 不是嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.55,1:20:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoveling out driveways, work in a car wash.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}鏟鏟車道 洗洗車子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.49,1:20:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any of that appeal to you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這類事情很吸引你?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.79,1:20:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have let you fuck up my life so far...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}到現在我一直讓你糟蹋我的生活...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.69,1:20:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I am not going to let you fuck this up.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這次我不會再讓你糟蹋了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.26,1:21:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. Forest Service.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}晚安 森林服務台{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.13,1:21:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Dick Hallorann.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我叫迪克·霍洛朗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.76,1:21:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the head chef at the Overlook Hotel.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是遙望旅館的廚師長{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.40,1:21:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. What can I do for you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}晚安 有什麼我能為您效勞嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.73,1:21:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trying to make an urgent phone call up there...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我一直想打個電話到那上面去 很急...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.50,1:21:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the operator said that the phone lines are down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但接線員告訴我線路不通{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.01,1:21:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of lines around here are down due to the storm.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這周圍的很多線路在暴風雪裏都斷掉了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.81,1:21:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to put you through any trouble...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不想給您帶來任何麻煩...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.68,1:22:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but there's a family up there all by themselves with a young kid.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但現在有一家人孤零零的在上頭 還帶著個小孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.12,1:22:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with this storm and everything...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}又遇到了這場暴風雪 總之...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.99,1:22:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'd appreciate it if you'd give them a call on your radio...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果您能用無線電聯繫上他們的話 我會非常感激的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.09,1:22:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just to see if everything's okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只是想看看是不是一切正常{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.60,1:22:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be glad to do that.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我很樂意這麼做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.10,1:22:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you call me back in about 20 minutes?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你為什麼不20分鐘後再打給我呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.10,1:22:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much. I'll do that.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}非常感謝 我會那樣做的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.34,1:22:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.09,1:22:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, Mr. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}晚安 特朗斯先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.26,1:22:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}晚安{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.29,1:23:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Lloyd.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗨 羅伊德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.96,1:23:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Been away, but now I'm back.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}離開了一陣子 但現在我又回來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.10,1:23:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, Mr. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}晚安 特朗斯先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.50,1:23:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}見到你真好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.70,1:23:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to be back, Lloyd.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}回來真不錯 羅伊德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.01,1:23:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll it be, sir?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}來點什麼呢 先生?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.54,1:23:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair of the dog that bit me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那只咬過我的狗 它身上的毛 (注: 以毒攻毒之意){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.21,1:23:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bourbon on the rocks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}加冰的波本酒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.72,1:23:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll do her.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就這麼辦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.64,1:23:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No charge to you, Mr. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不收您的錢 特朗斯先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.34,1:23:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No charge?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不收錢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.94,1:23:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your money's no good here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}您的錢在這裏用不上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.58,1:23:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orders from the house.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是房子的命令{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.52,1:24:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orders from the house.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}房子的命令{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.26,1:24:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink up, Mr. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}喝光吧 特朗斯先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.47,1:24:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the kind of man likes to know who's buying their drinks, Lloyd.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是那種喜歡知道 是誰在幫誰買酒的人 羅伊德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.31,1:24:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a matter that concerns you, Mr. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那與你無關 特朗斯先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.45,1:24:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, not at this point.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}至少 在這點上無關{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.19,1:24:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything you say, Lloyd.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}隨你怎麼說 羅伊德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.02,1:24:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything you say.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}隨你怎麼說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.01,1:24:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear! I'm so sorry, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}噢 天啊! 我真的很抱歉 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.58,1:24:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear. Oh, dear.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}噢 我的天!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.25,1:24:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made an awful mess of your jacket, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我把您的夾克弄得一團糟 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.05,1:24:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. I've got plenty of jackets.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}沒關係 我有很多的夾克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.89,1:25:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid it's advocaat, sir. It tends to stain.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但這是蛋酒 先生 它常常會留下污點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.89,1:25:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advocaat, is it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}蛋酒 是嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.23,1:25:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. I think the best thing...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 先生 我想最好的辦法...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.60,1:25:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is to come along to the gentlemen's room...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就是去男洗手間...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.00,1:25:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and we'll get some water to it, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然後我們用水擦一下 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.37,1:25:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you might have got a spot of it on yourself...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看起來好像你身上也沾了一點...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.88,1:25:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jeevesy old boy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}傑佛西老夥計{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.08,1:25:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter, sir. You're the important one.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那沒關係 先生 您比較重要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.55,1:25:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awfully nice of you to say.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你這麼說真是太好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.38,1:25:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I intended to change my jacket this evening...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}當然 我想過在晚會前{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.46,1:25:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...before the fish and goose soiree.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}換件夾克...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.92,1:25:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very wise, sir. Very wise.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很明智 先生 非常明智{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.16,1:25:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. I'll just...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這兒 我幫你...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.30,1:25:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...hold this for you there, Jeevesy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拿著這個 傑佛西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.77,1:25:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir. Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}先生 謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.60,1:25:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see if we can improve this with a little water, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看看沾點水是不是會好些 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.44,1:25:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll just...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好吧 我把...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.91,1:25:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...set my bourbon and advocaat down right there.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的波本酒和蛋酒放在這兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.68,1:25:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't keep you a moment.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}耽誤不了您不多久時間{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.32,1:25:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.79,1:25:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do they call you, Jeevesy?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他們是怎麼叫你的呢 傑佛西?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.66,1:25:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grady, sir. Delbert Grady.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}格瑞第 先生 戴伯特·格瑞第{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.00,1:26:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grady?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}格瑞第?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.03,1:26:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.54,1:26:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delbert Grady.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}戴伯特·格瑞第{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.07,1:26:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}對 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.32,1:26:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grady...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}格瑞第先生...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.52,1:26:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...haven't I seen you somewhere before?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我該不會以前在哪兒見過你吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.82,1:26:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, no, sir. I don't believe so.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}為什麼...? 不是 先生 我不這麼認為{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.57,1:26:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming off now, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}擦掉了 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.34,1:26:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grady...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}格瑞第先生...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.41,1:26:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...weren't you once the caretaker here?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不是曾經擔任過這裏的看管員嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.08,1:26:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, no, sir. I don't believe so.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}為什麼...? 不是 先生 我不這麼認為{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.92,1:26:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You a married man, are you, Mr. Grady?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你結婚了 是嗎 格瑞第先生?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.46,1:26:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.49,1:26:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a wife and two daughters, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我有妻子和兩個女兒 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.80,1:27:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.00,1:27:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...where are they now?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她們現在在哪裏?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.47,1:27:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're somewhere around. I'm not quite sure at the moment.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她們就在附近的某個地方 我現在也不能確定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.72,1:27:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grady...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}格瑞第先生...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.22,1:27:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the caretaker here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你曾是這裏的看管員{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.09,1:27:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recognize you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我認出你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.46,1:27:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw your picture in the newspapers.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我在報紙上看到過你的照片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.97,1:27:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.20,1:27:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...chopped your wife and daughter up into little bits.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}把你的妻子和女兒剁成碎片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.24,1:27:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然後...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.28,1:27:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then you blew your brains out.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你把你自己的腦袋轟掉了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.12,1:27:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那真奇怪 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.89,1:27:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any recollection of that at all.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我對這個完全沒有一點印象{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.30,1:28:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grady...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}格瑞第先生...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.60,1:28:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you were the caretaker here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你曾是這裏的看管員{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.75,1:28:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to differ with you, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很抱歉我和你不一樣 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.39,1:28:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是你...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.86,1:28:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are the caretaker.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}才是看管員{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.96,1:28:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been the caretaker.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你一直都是看管員{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.77,1:28:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should know, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我應該知道 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.04,1:28:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我一直都在這裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.86,1:28:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know, Mr. Torrance...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道嗎 特朗斯先生...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.30,1:28:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that your son...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的兒子...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.47,1:29:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is attempting to bring an outside party...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}正試圖帶外面的一幫人...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.37,1:29:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...into this situation?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}加入到這裏來?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.15,1:29:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道這個嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.09,1:29:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is, Mr. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他正是 特朗斯先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.53,1:29:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}誰?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.93,1:29:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A nigger.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一個黑鬼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.64,1:29:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A nigger?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一個黑鬼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.78,1:29:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A nigger...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一個黑鬼...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.41,1:29:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...cook.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}廚子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.02,1:29:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎麼帶法?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.56,1:29:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your son...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的兒子...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.76,1:29:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has a very great talent.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有一種非常好的天賦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.53,1:29:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you are aware how great it is.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我認為你都不知道那有多高{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.77,1:29:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he is attempting to use that very talent...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但他正在試圖使用他的天賦...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.21,1:29:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...against your will.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}用來反抗你的意旨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.72,1:30:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.76,1:30:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he is a very willful boy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他是個很任性的孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.23,1:30:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed he is, Mr. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他的確是 特朗斯先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.83,1:30:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A very willful boy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一個非常任性的孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.94,1:30:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rather...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一個很...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.47,1:30:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...naughty boy...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}頑皮的孩子...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.21,1:30:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if I may be so bold, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果允許我大膽的說 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.65,1:30:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's his mother.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那是她媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.56,1:30:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.23,1:30:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...interferes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}妨礙我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.33,1:30:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps they need a good...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}也許需要跟他們好好的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.64,1:30:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...talking-to.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}談一談{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.67,1:30:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.71,1:30:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you don't mind my saying so.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不介意我這麼說的話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.28,1:30:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}也許...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.45,1:31:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a bit more.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}光談還不夠{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.35,1:31:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My girls, sir...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的姑娘們 先生...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.79,1:31:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they didn't care for the Overlook at first.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她們開始不喜歡遙望旅館{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.26,1:31:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them actually stole a pack of matches...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}其中一個最後偷了包火柴...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.36,1:31:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and tried to burn it down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}想把旅館燒了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.10,1:31:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是我...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.97,1:31:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...corrected them, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}糾正了她們 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.27,1:31:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when my wife tried to prevent me from doing my duty...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}當我的妻子阻止我 達成我的使命的時候...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.61,1:31:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.88,1:31:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...corrected her.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}糾正了她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.23,1:31:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have the Snowcat.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們有雪地車{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.57,1:31:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the weather breaks...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果天氣稍微變好...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.54,1:31:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we might just be able...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們就能...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.51,1:31:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to get down the mountain.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}下山去了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.25,1:32:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could call the forest rangers first...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我可以先給林務員打電話...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.42,1:32:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and...tell them that we're coming...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}告訴他們我們來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.29,1:32:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,....so that...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這樣...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.66,1:32:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they could start searching for us in case we didn't make it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果我們後來沒到達 他們就會來找我們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.54,1:32:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if Jack won't come with us...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果傑克不陪我們走的話...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.17,1:32:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll just have to tell him that we're going by ourselves.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我只有告訴他 我們自己走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.11,1:32:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就這麼辦了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.45,1:32:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Redrum.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}Redrum紅酒 (注:謀殺-Murder的倒寫){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.92,1:32:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Redrum.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}Redrum紅酒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.83,1:32:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, hon?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎麼了 寶貝?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.20,1:32:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Redrum!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}Redrum紅酒!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.30,1:32:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you having a bad dream?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在做惡夢嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.31,1:32:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hon?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}寶貝?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.35,1:33:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Danny's not here, Mrs. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}丹尼不在這兒 特朗斯太太{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.26,1:33:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, honey.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快點 寶貝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.77,1:33:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}醒醒啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.14,1:33:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just had a bad dream.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你只是做了個惡夢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.81,1:33:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}沒事了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.01,1:33:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Danny can't wake up, Mrs. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}丹尼不能醒來了 特朗斯太太{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.36,1:33:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}醒醒!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.33,1:33:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.87,1:33:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就現在{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.87,1:33:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}醒醒!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.28,1:33:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Danny's gone away, Mrs. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}丹尼離開了 特朗斯太太{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.43,1:34:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is KDK 1 calling KDK 12.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}KDK 1 呼叫 KDK 12{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.50,1:34:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KDK 1 calling KDK 12.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}KDK 1 呼叫 KDK 12{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.74,1:34:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you receiving me?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你有收到嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.71,1:34:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is KDK 1 calling KDK 12.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}KDK 1 呼叫 KDK 12{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.51,1:34:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KDK 1 calling KDK 12.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}KDK 1 呼叫 KDK 12{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.52,1:34:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you read me?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}聽到我說話嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.56,1:34:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is KDK 1 calling KDK 12.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}KDK 1 呼叫 KDK 12{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.79,1:34:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KDK 1 calling KDK 12.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}KDK 1 呼叫 KDK 12{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.56,1:34:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you receiving me?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你有收到嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.77,1:35:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. Forest service.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}晚安 森林服務台{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.84,1:35:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Dick Hallorann again.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我還是迪克·霍洛朗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.28,1:35:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called a while ago about the folks at the Overlook Hotel.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我剛才打了電話聯繫遙望旅館的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.62,1:35:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We tried to contact them several times but they didn't answer.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們試圖聯繫他們多次 但都沒有回應{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.62,1:35:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they got their radio turned off or they can't hear it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可能他們沒有開無線電 也可能是沒聽到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.43,1:35:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, I'd be glad to try again later on.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果你覺得有必要 我待會兒再呼叫他們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.83,1:35:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very nice of you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你人真好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.17,1:35:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you back later.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我一會兒再打給你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.14,1:35:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}再見{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.26,1:36:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, miss. What time will we get to Denver?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}對不起 小姐 我們什麼時候才能到丹佛?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.50,1:36:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're due to arrive at 8:20, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}預計是8點20分到達 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.87,1:36:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}非常感謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.38,1:37:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Durkin's Garage.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}杜瑞凱的修車場{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.51,1:37:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I speak to Larry?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我找賴利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.85,1:37:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}請說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.11,1:37:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Larry. This is Dick. Dick Hallorann.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗨 賴利 我是迪克 迪克·霍洛朗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.88,1:37:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dick! How you doing?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}迪克! 你好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.75,1:37:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the weather down there?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那邊天氣怎麼樣?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.32,1:37:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in Florida. I'm calling from Stapleton Airport.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我沒在佛羅里達 我在斯塔普列頓機場給你打電話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.86,1:37:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing there?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在那兒幹什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.89,1:37:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got in from Miami. I got to get to the Overlook today.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我剛從邁阿密來 我今天要去遙望旅館{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.53,1:37:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the weather like there?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那裏天氣如何?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.80,1:38:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The snowplows are keeping things moving in town...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}掃雪機不斷在運作 貨物還是能運進城...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.87,1:38:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the mountain roads are blocked.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是山路全被封死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.34,1:38:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm going to need a Snowcat to get up there.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那我找輛雪地車上去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.24,1:38:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you fix me up with one?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你能給我弄出一輛嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.28,1:38:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal about getting there today...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}出了什麼大事 非得今天上那兒...?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.58,1:38:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...especially in this weather?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}尤其是在這種天氣?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.02,1:38:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Larry, just between you and me, we got a very serious problem...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}賴利 只在你我之間說說 我們遇上了很嚴重的問題...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.69,1:38:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with the people taking care of the place.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}關於看管那個地方的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.13,1:38:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They turned out to be completely unreliable assholes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他們根本就在打混摸魚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.20,1:38:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ullman phoned me last night.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}尤爾曼先生昨晚給我打了電話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.20,1:38:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm supposed to find out if they have to be replaced.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}委派我去看看 是不是該把他們換掉! ?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.04,1:38:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will it take you to get here?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要多久你才能到那裏?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.41,1:38:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About five hours.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}大概五小時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.28,1:38:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to rent a car here at the airport.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我會在機場租輛車{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.01,1:38:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll take care of it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好 雪地車我會想辦法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.95,1:38:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Larry. I really appreciate that.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}謝謝 賴利 我真的非常感激{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.99,1:38:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. Drive carefully.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就這樣吧 開車小心些{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.29,1:38:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're with Hal and Charlie on Radio 63, KHOW, Denver.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}您正在收聽的是丹佛63號電台 哈爾和查理為您播報{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.76,1:38:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we have a bad day out there.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天氣很糟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.54,1:38:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy snow throughout the Denver metro area.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}丹佛市中區普降大雪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.11,1:39:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many mountain passes...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很多的入山關口...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.81,1:39:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... Wolf Creek and Red Mountain passes are closed...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}狼溪和紅山的關口被關閉...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.88,1:39:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the chain law is in effect at the Eisenhower Tunnel.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}連帶也影響了艾森豪威爾隧道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.38,1:39:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hear from the news department...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們從新聞部門獲悉...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.25,1:39:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...only a few flights are landing at Stapleton Airport...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只有少數幾架飛機 降落在斯塔普列頓機場...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.66,1:39:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and with storms like this...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而且在這樣的暴風雪天氣...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.46,1:39:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I guess the entire airport will be closed within the hour.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想機場會在一個小時內 完全關閉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.76,1:39:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The storm will continue through the day and the Weather Service...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}暴風雪會持續一整天 氣象局...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.83,1:39:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has declared a stockman's and traveler's advisory...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}已發佈了 針對所有丹佛城周邊地區的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.50,1:39:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for all areas outlying the Denver metro region.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}旅客和牧人的通告{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.51,1:39:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the cows in the barn.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}把乳牛關在棚裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.37,1:39:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hon?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}寶貝?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.41,1:39:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me for a minute, will you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}聽我說 就一分鐘 好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.65,1:40:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to go and talk to Daddy for a few minutes...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要去和爸爸談幾分鐘...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.55,1:40:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I'll be right back.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我會很快回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.56,1:40:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to just stay here...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要你就待在這兒...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.29,1:40:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and watch your cartoons, okay?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看你的動畫片 好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.90,1:40:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, hon?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好嗎 寶貝?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.67,1:40:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mrs. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好 特朗斯太太{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.32,1:40:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.59,1:40:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back in just about five minutes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我大概只要五分鐘就回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.29,1:40:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to lock the door behind me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我出去的時候會把門給鎖上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.55,1:42:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只有工作 沒有玩樂 傑克呆若木雞!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.03,1:43:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只有工作 沒有玩樂 傑克呆若木雞!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.00,1:44:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你說好不好呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.31,1:44:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好不好呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.79,1:44:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing down here?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在這下面做什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.83,1:44:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我只是...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.64,1:44:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wanted...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}想...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.11,1:44:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to talk to you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}和你談談{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.21,1:44:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.08,1:44:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那我們就談吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.36,1:45:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to talk about?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你想談什麼呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.27,1:45:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really remember.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我真的是記不得了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.24,1:45:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't remember.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你記不得了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.18,1:45:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不行...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.88,1:45:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can't.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不能{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.59,1:45:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was about Danny?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}也許是關於丹尼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.23,1:45:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was about him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}也許是關於他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.57,1:45:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should discuss Danny.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想我們該討論一下丹尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.68,1:45:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.88,1:45:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we should discuss what should be done with him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們該討論一下 應該拿他怎麼辦才好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.35,1:45:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should be done with him?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}應該拿他怎麼辦?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.93,1:46:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.23,1:46:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's true.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我認為那不是真的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.44,1:46:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you have some very definite ideas...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想你有一些很明確的想法...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.24,1:46:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...about what should be done with Danny.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}關於應該拿丹尼怎麼辦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.14,1:46:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd like to know what they are.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想知道究竟是些什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.65,1:46:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯 我...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.75,1:46:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think maybe he should be taken to a doctor.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想也許該帶他去看醫生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.35,1:46:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think "maybe" he should be taken to a doctor?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你認為"也許"該帶他去看醫生?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.89,1:46:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When do you think "maybe" he should be taken to a doctor?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是什麼時候開始想 "也許"該帶他去看醫生的?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.87,1:46:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as possible?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}盡快?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.83,1:46:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"As soon as possible?"\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"盡快? "{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.84,1:46:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}求求你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.68,1:46:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe his health might be at stake.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你相信他的健康有嚴重問題?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.52,1:46:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.39,1:46:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are concerned about him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而且你很關心他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.59,1:46:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And are you concerned about me?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那你關心我嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.66,1:46:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我當然關心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.03,1:47:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you are!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你當然關心!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.47,1:47:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever thought about my responsibilities?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你可曾想過我的責任嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.80,1:47:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在說些什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.51,1:47:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever had a single moment's...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你有沒有想過 就一分鐘...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.54,1:47:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...thought about my responsibilities?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}想過我的責任?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.81,1:47:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever thought for a single moment...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有沒有片刻想過...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.28,1:47:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...about my responsibilities to my employers?!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我對我的僱主的責任? !{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.35,1:47:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has is ever occurred to you...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我已經同意...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.39,1:47:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I have agreed to look after the hotel until May 1st?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看管這座旅館直到5月1號?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.13,1:47:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it matter to you at all...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它跟你有關係嗎...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.36,1:47:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the owners have placed their complete confidence in me...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就是主人完全信任我...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.67,1:47:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that I have signed a letter of agreement...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就是我簽了契約...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.00,1:47:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in which I've accepted that responsibility?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在那裏面我接受了委任?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.07,1:47:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have the slightest idea...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是否有哪怕是最卑微的一點理解...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.31,1:47:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what a moral and ethical principal is? Do you?!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}關於什麼是倫理道德的精髓? 你有嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.91,1:47:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has it ever occurred to you what would happen to my future...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你可曾想過 會對我的前途產生什麼影響...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.22,1:47:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if I fail to live up to my responsibilities?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果我不能帶著我的責任快樂的生活?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.82,1:47:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has it ever occurred to you? Has it?!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你可曾想過那樣的事? 可曾想過? !{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.32,1:47:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}走開!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.73,1:47:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}為什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.09,1:47:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to go back to my room.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想回我的房間了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.26,1:47:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}為什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.17,1:47:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.17,1:48:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm very confused.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我很困惑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.34,1:48:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I just need a chance to think things over.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我需要找個機會把事情想清楚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.04,1:48:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had your whole fucking life to think things over!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你可以用他媽的一輩子時間 去把事情想清楚!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.18,1:48:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good's a few minutes more going to do you now?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}現在這幾分鐘又怎麼夠用?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.92,1:48:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}走開!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.76,1:48:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}求求你!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.83,1:48:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hurt me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}別傷害我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.09,1:48:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to hurt you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不會傷害你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.63,1:48:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}走開!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.03,1:48:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}走開!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.10,1:48:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}親愛的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.30,1:48:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light of my life.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我生命的亮光{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.30,1:48:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to hurt you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不會傷害你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.84,1:48:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't let me finish my sentence.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不讓我說完{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.04,1:48:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, "I'm not going to hurt you."\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我說: "我不會傷害你"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.44,1:48:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to bash your brains in.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我只想錘你的頭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.48,1:48:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bash them right the fuck in.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我只想一邊辦事一邊重錘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.52,1:48:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}走開!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.59,1:48:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}走開!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.82,1:48:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to hurt you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不會傷害你{\r}
