Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.26,1:48:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}走開!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.19,1:48:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}求求你!{\r}
