Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.43,1:48:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}走開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.47,1:48:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put that bat down, Wendy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}把那根球棒放下 溫蒂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.97,1:48:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}停下來!{\r}
