Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.52,1:49:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the bat.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}把球棒給我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.92,1:49:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}走開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.43,1:49:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Stop it! - Give me the bat.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 停下來! - 把球棒給我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.20,1:49:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}見鬼!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.52,1:50:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在幹什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.02,1:50:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.89,1:50:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在幹什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.73,1:50:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在幹什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.85,1:51:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.72,1:51:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在幹什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.56,1:51:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the door!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}開門{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.59,1:51:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn it!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}見鬼!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.83,1:51:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out of here! Open the goddamn door!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}讓我出去! 開門!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.10,1:51:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy, listen.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}溫蒂 聽著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.77,1:51:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out and I'll forget the whole goddamn thing.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}讓我出去 我會把整件事忘掉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.91,1:51:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be just like nothing ever happened.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就當什麼也沒有發生過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.06,1:51:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}寶貝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.63,1:51:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you hurt my head real bad.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想你真的對我的頭下了重手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.54,1:51:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dizzy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我頭昏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.21,1:51:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need a doctor.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我需要個醫生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.28,1:52:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}甜心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.16,1:52:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me in here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}別把我留在這兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.10,1:52:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我現在要走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.07,1:52:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to try...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我今天要...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.11,1:52:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to get Danny down the Sidewinder...in the Snowcat today.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}用雪地車帶丹尼下山...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.42,1:52:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring back a doctor.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我會帶個醫生回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.05,1:52:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}溫蒂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.63,1:52:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我現在要走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:41.50,1:52:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Wendy. - yes?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 溫蒂 - 幹嘛?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.94,1:52:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a big surprise coming to you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你會有個大驚喜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.21,1:52:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going anywhere.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你哪兒都去不了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.48,1:53:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go check out the Snowcat and the radio, and you'll see what I mean.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}去看看雪地車吧 還有無線電 你會明白我的意思的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.23,1:53:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go check it out.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}去看看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.06,1:53:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go check it out!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}去看看!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.64,1:53:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go check it out.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}去看看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.43,1:55:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Grady, Mr. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是格瑞第 特朗斯先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.57,1:55:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delbert Grady.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}德爾伯特·格瑞第{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.11,1:55:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grady?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}格瑞第?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.07,1:55:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Grady.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你好 格瑞第{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.57,1:55:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Torrance...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}特朗斯先生...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.31,1:55:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I see you can hardly have taken care of the...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我看你很難辦好...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.78,1:55:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...business we discussed.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我們先前討論的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.99,1:56:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to rub it in, Mr. Grady.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}沒有必要說第二遍 格瑞第先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.80,1:56:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deal with that situation as soon as I get out of here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只要我一出去 就會處理現在的情況{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.74,1:56:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you indeed, Mr. Torrance?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你確實會 特朗斯先生?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.97,1:56:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.98,1:56:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my doubts.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我有幾個疑點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.28,1:56:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, and others, have come to believe...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我 還有其他人 都相信...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.72,1:56:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that your heart is not in this.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的心沒在這裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.36,1:56:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you haven't the belly for it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你對它沒胃口{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.07,1:56:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give me one more chance to prove it, Mr. Grady.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}再給我個機會證明它 格瑞第先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.21,1:56:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I ask.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那是我全部的要求{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.68,1:56:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wife appears to be stronger than we imagined, Mr. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的妻子看來比我們想像要來得強 特朗斯先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.15,1:56:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhat more...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要更...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.82,1:56:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...resourceful.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}機靈一點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.06,1:56:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to have got the better of you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好像她勝過你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.06,1:56:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the moment, Mr. Grady.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就這一會兒 格瑞第先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.47,1:57:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only for the moment.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就只這一會兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.54,1:57:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fear you will have to deal with this matter...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我怕你得用一種最粗野的方式...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.98,1:57:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the harshest possible way, Mr. Torrance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}來處理這件事 特朗斯先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.21,1:57:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fear...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我怕...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.05,1:57:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that is the only thing to do.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}這是唯一可做的事了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.09,1:57:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I look forward to...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}再沒有比這...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.39,1:57:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with greater pleasure, Mr. Grady.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}更讓人愉快的事 格瑞第先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.70,1:57:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You give your word on that, do you, Mr. Torrance?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你保證 不是嗎 特朗斯先生?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.90,1:57:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give you my word.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我向你保證{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.06,1:58:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Redrum.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}Redrum紅酒 (注:Murder謀殺的倒寫){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.56,1:58:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Redrum.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}Redrum紅酒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:00.11,2:01:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Danny, stop it!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}丹尼 別這樣!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.48,2:01:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我回家了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.29,2:02:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, come out, wherever you are.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}出來 出來 不管你在哪兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:05.73,2:03:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get out.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我出不去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:08.40,2:03:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快跑!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:10.36,2:03:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run and hide!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快跑 躲起來!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:12.34,2:03:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快跑!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.67,2:03:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:16.61,2:03:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little pigs, little pigs, let me come in.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}小豬 小豬 讓我進去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:26.88,2:03:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not by the hair on your chinny-chin-chin?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不用你下巴上的毛?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:31.82,2:03:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll huff...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然後我要生氣了...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.09,2:03:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I'll puff...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}接著我要喘氣了...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.20,2:03:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I'll blow your house in!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然後我要毀了你的房子 衝進去!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:53.18,2:03:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}求求你!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:55.29,2:03:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:57.72,2:03:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:17.84,2:04:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}停下來!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:23.32,2:04:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's Johnny!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}強尼來了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:06.84,2:07:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}喂?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:13.52,2:07:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody here?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有人在嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:37.38,2:07:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}喂?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:51.26,2:07:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody here?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有人在嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:08:23.06,2:08:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody here?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有人在嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:06.01,2:09:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Danny-boy!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}丹尼男孩!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:48.57,2:11:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我來了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:53.01,2:11:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming, Dan!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我來了 小丹!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:55.75,2:12:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great party, isn't it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}爽死人的宴會 不是嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:13:15.80,2:13:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我來了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:13:20.61,2:13:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你逃不掉的!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:13:26.78,2:13:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right behind you!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我就在你後面!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:17:27.66,2:17:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mommy! - Danny, come here!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 媽咪! - 丹尼 到這兒來!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:17:30.90,2:17:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}媽咪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:17:40.98,2:17:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where...?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在哪...?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:18:37.26,2:18:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}溫蒂!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:18:39.75,2:18:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等等!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:18:52.27,2:18:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:18:54.27,2:18:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}救命!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:19:06.76,2:19:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}溫蒂!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:19:11.75,2:19:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}救救我!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:19:15.25,2:19:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}求你...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:19:17.24,2:19:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}溫蒂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:19:20.81,2:19:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}救命{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:19:23.30,2:19:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}求求你{\r}
